These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-1::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: photography, writing, hiking
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: sports, scientific, adventure
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: house, metal, hip-hop
The people use 3 different means of transport: roller, quad-bike, snowmobile
1. the person driving the roller is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
2. the fan of house is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
3. the person who's hobby is photography is between the person watching scientific movies and the person watching adventure movies##2
4. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
5. the fan of hip-hop is the person watching scientific movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| Hobby         | writing | photography   | hiking   |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific     | sports | adventure |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop  | house    | metal      |
| Transport     | quad-bike     | roller      | snowmobile |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-2::.
There 3 different types of food: grapes, asparagus, orange
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: country, hip-hop, punk
There are 3 different nationalities: dutch, thai, nigerian
3 different pets are kept: rat, pony, cat
1. the fan of punk is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
2. the nigerian is on the left of the fan of punk##1
3. the person eating asparagus is the nigerian##1
4. the person eating grapes is the thai##1
5. the owner of the rat is between the fan of hip-hop and the person eating orange##2
6. the person eating orange is the owner of the pony##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3      |
| Food          | asparagus  | grapes     | orange     |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop     | punk     | country      |
| Nationality   | nigerian  | thai | dutch |
| Pet           | cat | rat     | pony       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-3::.
There 3 different types of food: watermelon, cranberry, plum
The people have 3 different jobs:  designer, electrician, scientist
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: family, action, comedy
3 different pets are kept: rabbit, horse, hamster
1. the designer is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
2. the owner of the rabbit is between the scientist and the person watching comedy movies##2
3. the person eating watermelon is on the far left##1
4. the owner of the horse is the person eating cranberry##1
5. the owner of the rabbit is the person watching action movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |
| Food          | watermelon  | plum     | cranberry     |
| Job           | scientist | designer  | electrician   |
| Movie-Genre   | family  | action    | comedy |
| Pet           | hamster     | rabbit | horse |

