.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-4::.
There 3 different types of food: strawberry, asparagus, blueberry
The people have 3 different jobs:  nurse, writer, manager
3 different pets are kept: ferret, lizard, dog
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cycling, golf, badminton
1. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
2. the person eating asparagus is on the right of the manager##1
3. the person eating blueberry is between the writer and the owner of the ferret##2
4. the person eating asparagus is the person who's sport is golf##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3      |
| Food    | strawberry       | blueberry  | asparagus   |
| Job     | writer    | manager  | nurse |
| Pet     | lizard   | dog | ferret        |
| Sport   | badminton | cycling     | golf      |

