.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-5::.
There 3 different types of food: spinach, pepper, asparagus
The people have 3 different hobbies: gardening, skydiving, woodworking
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: techno, dubstep, reggae
3 different pets are kept: snake, hedgehog, horse
1. the fan of reggae is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
2. the owner of the snake is between the fan of reggae and the person who's hobby is woodworking##2
3. the person who's hobby is gardening is the owner of the hedgehog##1
4. the person eating spinach is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
5. the owner of the snake is on the left of the person eating pepper##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Food          | asparagus    | spinach     | pepper      |
| Hobby         | gardening | skydiving | woodworking |
| Music-Genre   | reggae  | dubstep       | techno       |
| Pet           | hedgehog     | snake       | horse     |

