1. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
2. the person eating blueberry is the person who's hobby is camping##1
3. the fan of folk is between the person eating mango and the owner of the pony##2
4. the fan of salsa is on the far right##1
5. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |
| Food          | mango | raspberry | blueberry    |
| Hobby         | board-games | woodworking      | camping |
| Music-Genre   | jazz   | folk     | salsa        |
| Pet           | bird      | hamster       | pony      |

