The people have 3 different hobbies: dancing, singing, puzzles
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: musical, epic, time-travel
The people use 3 different means of transport: ship, taxi, trike
1. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
2. the person who's hobby is singing is between the person eating mango and the person driving the ship##2
3. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person eating pear##1
4. the person driving the ship is on the far right##1
5. the person who's hobby is singing is between the person who's hobby is puzzles and the person watching musical movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |     3     |
| Food          | mango      | pear   | kiwi |
