The people have 3 different hobbies: magic-tricks, collecting, gardening
The people have 3 different jobs:  chef, security-guard, doctor
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: soul, disco, blues
1. the doctor is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the fan of disco##1
3. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
4. the chef is between the person who's hobby is collecting and the person drinking mirinda##2
5. the person drinking 7up is the fan of blues##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |     3      |
| Beverage      | lemonade       | 7up      | mirinda      |
| Hobby         | collecting    | gardening | magic-tricks      |
| Job           | doctor | chef     | security-guard |
| Music-Genre   | disco     | blues          | soul       |

