.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-9::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, hot-chocolate, mirinda
There 3 different types of food: lettuce, apple, corn
There are 3 different nationalities: argentine, polish, thai
The people use 3 different means of transport: subway, motorbike, scooter
1. the person driving the scooter is between the polish and the thai##2
2. the person eating corn is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far left##1
4. the person eating apple is on the far left##1
5. the argentine is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
6. the person driving the motorbike is the polish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |    3     |
| Beverage      | iced-tea      | hot-chocolate | mirinda     |
| Food          | apple   | lettuce      | corn     |
| Nationality   | thai  | argentine      | polish |
| Transport     | subway | scooter        | motorbike     |

