.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-10::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: collecting, board-games, singing
The people have 3 different jobs:  police-officer, lawyer, dancer
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cricket, baseball, soccer
The people use 3 different means of transport: quad-bike, subway, helicopter
1. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
2. the lawyer is between the police-officer and the person who's hobby is board-games##2
3. the person who's sport is soccer is the person who's hobby is singing##1
4. the person who's sport is baseball is the dancer##1
5. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the police-officer##1
6. the person driving the quad-bike is the person who's sport is baseball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |        2        |    3     |
| Hobby       | board-games       | singing       | collecting    |
| Job         | dancer | lawyer | police-officer |
| Sport       | baseball      | soccer         | cricket |
| Transport   | quad-bike        | helicopter            | subway  |

