1. the person drinking juice is on the left of the fan of classical##1
2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the australian##1
3. the british is in the middle##1
4. the british is between the person who's hobby is drawing and the person who's hobby is video-games##2
5. the fan of d&b is on the far left##1
6. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |      3      |
| Beverage      | juice     | almond-milk | tea      |
| Hobby         | drawing  | singing       | video-games |
| Music-Genre   | d&b   | classical         | pop     |
| Nationality   | indian | british    | australian     |

