2. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the software-developer##1
3. the musician is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
4. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
5. the person eating lemonademelon is the person watching superhero movies##1
6. the software-developer is on the right of the musician##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2        |       3       |
