.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-15::.
There 3 different types of food: pear, banana, apricot
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, reggae, pop
There are 3 different nationalities: canadian, thai, russian
The people use 3 different means of transport: roller, airplane, car
1. the fan of pop is on the left of the thai##1
2. the person driving the airplane is between the fan of pop and the russian##2
3. the person driving the roller is on the far right##1
4. the person eating banana is between the fan of pop and the person eating pear##2
5. the fan of reggae is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| Food          | apricot  | banana   | pear |
| Music-Genre   | pop  | reggae     | ambient |
| Nationality   | canadian | thai | russian   |
| Transport     | car   | airplane   | roller      |

