3. the fan of rock is the owner of the fish##1
4. the owner of the snake is the fan of ambient##1
5. the person driving the motorbike is the owner of the frog##1
6. the mexican is on the right of the person driving the trike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |
| Music-Genre   | rock | ambient  | house     |
| Nationality   | nigerian    | spanish | mexican |
| Pet           | fish        | snake   | frog  |
| Transport     | van      | trike   | motorbike |

