3. the person watching mystery movies is the owner of the fish##1
4. the architect is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
5. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far right##1
6. the teacher is between the nurse and the fan of soul##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |    3     |
