.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-19::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, cola, lemonade
The people have 3 different hobbies: fishing, reading, magic-tricks
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: d&b, indie, country
3 different pets are kept: cat, bird, chinchilla
1. the owner of the bird is the fan of country##1
2. the fan of indie is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
3. the fan of d&b is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person who's hobby is fishing##2
4. the fan of indie is the owner of the chinchilla##1
5. the owner of the cat is between the person drinking cola and the fan of indie##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |      2      |      3      |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | lemonade     | cola        |
| Hobby         | reading   | magic-tricks | fishing |
| Music-Genre   | indie        | d&b       | country      |
| Pet           | chinchilla           | cat    | bird       |

