.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-20::.
There 3 different types of food: tomato, artichoke, cherry
3 different pets are kept: snake, bird, lizard
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: skiing, swimming, water-polo
The people use 3 different means of transport: trike, bike, airplane
1. the person eating tomato is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
2. the owner of the bird is the person driving the trike##1
3. the person who's sport is swimming is the person driving the trike##1
4. the person who's sport is skiing is the person eating cherry##1
5. the owner of the lizard is between the person driving the airplane and the person who's sport is swimming##2
6. the person who's sport is water-polo is the person eating tomato##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |
| Food        | artichoke      | tomato | cherry |
| Pet         | bird     | lizard    | snake        |
| Sport       | swimming | water-polo   | skiing   |
| Transport   | trike          | bike     | airplane       |

 